NAME
       isa_tools - Add or remove isa device

SYNOPSIS
       ls [OPTION]... 

DESCRIPTION
       Mandatory arguments to long options are mandatory for short options too.

       -a, --adddev
              add isa device into driver list

       -r, --rmdev
              remove isa device from driver list

       -p, --ioport 
              io port address
              If you want to know the situation of io port, you can use the command "cat /proc/ioports".

       -q, --irq
              isa interrupt level
              If you want to know the situation of interrupt, you can use the command "cat /proc/interrupts".

       -d, --dma
              system dma number

       -n, --driname
              driver's name

       -m, --devname
              device's name

       -h, --help
              usage

       -v, --version
              version of this software


Device name      io port range             irq range           dma range           driver name             device name

PCM3718          match the switch       match the switch     match the switch       bio3718              pcm3718,pcm3718h
                                             (2~7)               (1, 3)                                  pcm3718hg,pcm3718ho

PCM3725          match the switch       match the switch          none              bio3725                   pcm3725
                                             (2~7)                                           

